description.narrative: This outcome is about increasing women's voices in developing appropriate infrastructure that is safe and accessbile--so this has elements of public safety, plus disaster preparedness and response as well as women's voice and participation. Work under this outcome brings together women leaders of market vendor associations with government planners to ensure that women's voices are included in the planning of infrastructure development.
